caption: One of the most cosy squares in Paris, wonderful architectural structure but very intimate. You could take coffee and croissant from boulangerie nearby, set on one a few branches and relax in tranquility.
Superb fountain the dog loved bathing in it üòÖüòÇ ‚Ä¶

Place Laveran has two modern fountains installed in 1995. They face the Val de Grace church! Small benches allow you to sit nearby and a bakery right next door allows you to eat while sitting on a bench, listening to the fountain flowing and admiring the majestic church in front of you.... What more could you ask for????...!!
